(json 10 (content "Hello All, I recently graduated with my PhD in computer science. My research interests are primarily in motivation systems, motivated agents, AGI, and cognitive robotics. In other words, I found this RFP very interesting but I stumbeled on this call a few days before the deadline and didn't get the opportunity to submit.
If any winners of this project want some extra volunteer help, please send me an invite to your team. As a new grad, building networks with other researchers that have a strong shared interest in research topics is pivotal."))
