(json 13 (content "The completed literature review from part 1 of this project can be found as a PDF, website and curated list at <a href=https://github.com/robert-haas/awesome-biomedical-knowledge-graphs rel=nofollow ugc>https://github.com/robert-haas/awesome-biomedical-knowledge-graphs</a>. The completed Python package from part 2 of this project can be found at&nbsp;<a href=https://github.com/robert-haas/kgw rel=nofollow ugc>https://github.com/robert-haas/kgw</a>, downloaded with pip from <a href=https://pypi.org/project/kgw rel=nofollow ugc>https://pypi.org/project/kgw</a>&nbsp;and its documenation is available at <a href=https://robert-haas.github.io/kgw-docs rel=nofollow ugc>https://robert-haas.github.io/kgw-docs</a>."))
