(json 31 (proposal_id "6082"))
(json 31 (content "The platform never reveals actual data, only synthetic data. Post synthetic data generation there are checks for PII leakage, etc. Plus all actions are fully audited to give platform users a measure of confidence. Finally Confidential Computing and Secure Enclaves are used for most executions and these hardware attestations are available as part of the audit trails. The AI agent will always ask for confirmation. He is an assistant the user is still the boss. And the agent will produce audit/ traceability for independent third party verification."))
