(json 38 (proposal_id "4779"))
(json 38 (content "That is the reason we're submitting this proposal to add these features along with building an end-to-end tool which would include these features. Currently multi-chat feature exists in our UI, where each chat system history is retained as well. Task automation is not currently implemented, but this will be using a multi-agent system using CrewAI and LangGraph for creating an automation module (Evaluate problem -&gt; generate sub-queries -&gt; ranking sub-queries -&gt; searching the web -&gt; similarity search -&gt; Prepare report).&nbsp;I did not understand what you mean when you say I didn't see anything multi-chat management, task automation, or document handling, these are proposed features for which we have a vanilla implementation and that is the reason for putting in this proposal to build a full-fledged tool, hope that answers your question? 😃&nbsp;"))
