(json 47 (proposal_id "6210"))
(json 47 (content "Hi Emotublockchain,the AI-powered assistant chatbot will be designed as a customizable system, allowing it to be tailored and trained for specific needs within the SingularityNET platform. This flexibility will enable it to provide precise answers to a wide range of queries, enhancing user engagement and satisfaction.
Currently, the SingularityNET ecosystem lacks an AI assistant, leading users to seek help on external platforms like Telegram. Our chatbot will address this gap, significantly improving user experience and retention by offering immediate support within the ecosystem.
While integration challenges are anticipated, our experienced team, deeply familiar with SingularityNET's architecture, is well-equipped to navigate and mitigate these obstacles."))
(json 47 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 47 (created_at "2024-06-11 12:17:24"))
(json 47 (updated_at "2024-06-11 12:17:24"))
(json 48 (comment_id "764"))
(json 48 (user_id "437"))
(json 48 (proposal_id "4752"))
(json 48 (content "To address currency volatility, we plan to support transactions using stablecoins such as USDT, which provide stability in value. For reducing transaction fees, we are considering Layer 2 solutions that enable faster and more cost-effective transactions, thereby enhancing payment efficiency on our platform. Thanks for your support!"))
