(json 49 (user_id "437"))
(json 49 (proposal_id "4752"))
(json 49 (content "Hi Emotublockchain, thanks for your question. We are committed to the security and privacy of our users' data through the implementation of advanced encryption, strict access controls, and comprehensive data anonymization techniques. These measures are designed to protect sensitive information and ensure adherence to global data protection standards."))
(json 49 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 49 (created_at "2024-06-11 08:38:06"))
(json 49 (updated_at "2024-06-11 08:38:06"))
(json 50 (comment_id "762"))
(json 50 (user_id "437"))
(json 50 (proposal_id "4752"))
(json 50 (content "Hello Gombilla, thank you for emphasizing the importance of data privacy and security. We acknowledge the sensitivity of data in influencer marketing. We are actively ensuring that our operations comply with GDPR and other relevant data protection laws to safeguard personal information. Our approach includes implementing comprehensive security measures such as advanced data anonymization techniques to protect individual privacy, utilizing state-of-the-art secure servers that adhere to international security standards, and conducting regular, thorough security assessments to proactively identify and mitigate potential vulnerabilities. These efforts are in line with our commitment to uphold stringent data protection regulations and ensure that our platform remains secure and trustworthy."))
(json 50 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 50 (created_at "2024-06-11 08:31:58"))
(json 50 (updated_at "2024-06-11 08:31:58"))
