(json 51 (proposal_id "5793"))
(json 51 (content "













The project will be conducted in Brazilian Portuguese. Although there are differences in Portuguese from different countries, everyone can understand the content perfectly despite these variations. To include the specific idiomatic differences of each Portuguese-speaking country, we would need a larger budget to hire translators from each region, which would make the project very expensive. However, as mentioned, choosing Brazilian Portuguese ensures that all participants can effectively and inclusively understand the content. Additionally, we are committed to maintaining engagement and interest over time through relevant and interactive content, tailored to the needs and feedback of the participants.





&nbsp;








"))
