(json 53 (content "Thank you so much, Gombilla! Really appreciate the feedback, and we have definitely thought about this during our development and ideation phase. We are committed to implementing robust security measures including state-of-the-art encryption, stringent access controls, and comprehensive regular audits to ensure compliance with data protection regulations like GDPR and CCPA. Your insight is invaluable, and we will continue to focus on strengthening our security framework to protect our users' data against any potential breaches or unauthorized access. (* One key callout is that, AIMate can be installed on your desktop as well, so local LLMs can be hosted on desktops as well, ensuring data doesn't leave your system at all. This is an alternative in case users do not want to use calendar and mail plugins). &nbsp; If you do like our project, please do support us and vote for us at <a href=https://voting.deepfunding.ai/ rel=nofollow ugc>https://voting.deepfunding.ai/</a> (<strong>New Projects &gt; Proposal 7 &gt; AIMate: A companion in productivity by Ahan M R</strong>). Looking forward to serving the SNET ecosystem."))
