(json 54 (content "Thank you for your comment! We are currently looking at a sprint-based development mechanism. I will be working on the research and the applied science problems in this project, and will also be overseeing initiatives on the full-stack and blockchain integrations as well. My Team mates will be very much focussed on building the frontend and backend development along with onboarding the LLMs and web plugin integrations as well. Two interns will be joining (1 Data Science Intern and 1 SDE Intern) us to help support the initiative to ensure the project is completed and delivered in 16-18 weeks time +/- 3 weeks. We have collaborated on projects before and delivered as well on other ecosystems, and we look forward to bring AIMate into SingularityNET ecosystem as well. If you do believe in us and support our project, please do vote for us on <a href=https://voting.deepfunding.ai/ rel=nofollow ugc>https://voting.deepfunding.ai/</a> <strong>(New Projects &gt; Proposal 7 &gt; AIMate: A companion in productivity by Ahan M R)</strong>"))
