(json 89 (proposal_id "6228"))
(json 89 (content "&nbsp;It's great to see a focus on engaging the Eastern community, as they represent significant potential for growth in the decentralized AI platform space. How do you plan to tailor your content to effectively resonate with each of these cultural audiences?&nbsp;"))
