(json 90 (comment_id "722"))
(json 90 (user_id "730"))
(json 90 (proposal_id "6263"))
(json 90 (content "Thank you for your questions!
1. <strong>Incompatibility:</strong>&nbsp;Since both protocols focus on decentralized AI model deployment, the primary task is to align API interfaces. If incompatibilities are found, we will handle it by converting data exchange formats to ensure smooth integration.
2.&nbsp;<strong>AI Model Integration:</strong>&nbsp;Yes, Quatern.ai can integrate any type of AI model, including LLMs. We have already considered some LLM-specific experiments; please see <a href=https://x.com/quatern_ai/status/1766855123446186184 rel=nofollow ugc>here</a> for more details.
We appreciate your interest and support!"))
