(json 101 (content "


&nbsp;









Thank you for your question. As this event focuses on educating and onboarding the Toronto community to SNET and Deep Funding, our team has the expertise to execute it independently. However, if funded, we will reach out to SNET staff for potential attendance or materials, should they see value in participating. Our KPIs and metrics will include the number of RSVPs, actual attendees, and the quality of feedback from participants.





"))
(json 101 (comment_votes "0"))
