(json 102 (comment_id "710"))
(json 102 (user_id "531"))
(json 102 (proposal_id "5810"))
(json 102 (content "Great question. We have extensive experience hosting events as part of OffChain Global, including two successful events this year for ICP blockchain and Cardano Catalyst. Our venue partners provide excellent locations and ample space. We are well-prepared to handle logistical challenges through meticulous planning and coordination, ensuring a seamless event experience.
Inclusivity and diversity are central to our mission. Our community of over 150 individuals from diverse backgrounds and expertise will ensure broad outreach. We actively promote inclusivity through our various marketing efforts.
Aligned with SingularityNET's values, our event will emphasize decentralized, democratic, and beneficial AI and educate about SNET &amp; deep funding vision and mission. We aim to foster a collaborative environment, contributing to SingularityNET's growth, particularly in Toronto, and encouraging ongoing engagement."))
