(json 144 (comment_id "668"))
(json 144 (user_id "786"))
(json 144 (proposal_id "6104"))
(json 144 (content "Thank you for such interesting questions!
Regarding your first question, members of our team have a very specific background in developing AI-driven image enhancement technologies, among them super-resolution. We leverage this experience to fine-tune our solution to medical imaging, where accuracy and reliability are key.
On the linguistic scope of the project, we are starting off with major languages spoken across Africa, namely English and French, which are widely used across the continent. At a later date, and as the project matures, we expect to broaden our capabilities by adding more languages, in line with regional needs and user feedback.
Partnerships: We are in active discussions with medical facilities from different African countries to ensure diversity in training data that will be representative of all data sets. Such partnerships are important for the development and fine-tuning of our AI models&nbsp;
As for the data storage for the examples provided by the users at the end, security is paramount; we would adopt encrypted cloud storage solutions that match standards, ensuring that both the patient and facility records are kept safe and private. This also facilitates scalability and accessibility, two key elements for wide adoption.
We are especially excited that this project could have enormous importance and look forward to your favorable vote. We assure you of our commitment to transparency and excellence as we develop and roll out this service."))
