(json 155 (content "Clement, &nbsp;fantastic project and team. It was a while ago, but in high school, my classmates and I visited a malaria treatment center in The Gambia. Malaria affects so many people of all ages and is a mortal threat to health. It's inspiring to see your project take form and I wish you every success."))
