(json 157 (proposal_id "5777"))
(json 157 (content "The purpose of the ideation pool is that it is Designed to support the preliminary stages of AI project development. This pool serves as a springboard for refining ideas and preparing them for more substantial funding rounds in the New Projects pool.
The development of an mvp is in our opinion the best method for refining ideas as is the objective of the ideation pool, this is because it allows for the testing and study of the very thing we intend to build. By completing the mvp early on, we are allowed more time to chat with possible users about how to make the platform most amicable, perhaps one of the most useful things one could do in the ideation phase.&nbsp;
&nbsp;"))
(json 157 (comment_votes "0"))
