(json 158 (proposal_id "5815"))
(json 158 (content "Hey Gombilla,
thanks for your comment! Most (if not all) interesting existing solutions are provided by large internet companies. I see the main advantage of an SNET-based model in not having to pay those companies by uploading your personal photos but instead directly paying for the AI service you're using. Additionally, there's the other usual advantages of such a decentralized solutions, e.g. community government over development of future features, open-source access to the code, etc. &nbsp;"))
(json 158 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 158 (created_at "2024-06-07 12:34:24"))
