(json 161 (content "Unfortunately there is no way to respond to an expert review, so I'll leave my comment here.
First of all, thanks for leaving a review and underlining the strengths of the team.
Regarding architecture, extensibility - we made a focus in our proposal on the product side. We've already released the solution for the STC graph (100+ million nodes, 1B+ edges), so our solution architecture (although for other db) is quite scalable.As shown in our demo - the usability we plan to cover by implementing nlp-to-cypherFrom a product perspective - we're focusing mostly on the product, as you may see from the whitepaper attached."))
(json 161 (comment_votes "0"))
