(json 164 (content "You raise a valid point about the critical importance of reliability and interpretability for healthcare AI systems like the NPP. We understand that for providers and patients to trust and act on the model's predictions. For reliability, the core language model is trained solely on medical terminology related to prescriptions, diagnoses, treatments, etc., limiting potential hallucinations in its generated outputs.For interpretability, the classification and explanation module highlights which input factors influenced the predictions most, while also providing plain language explanations of the forecasted medical events."))
