(json 179 (user_id "385"))
(json 179 (proposal_id "4734"))
(json 179 (content "Thanks for reviewing our project!
You&rsquo;re spot on. In the beginning, we struggled with video quality and consistency. But after two years, we&rsquo;ve nailed down a Lean workflow and solid guidelines for scripting, design, editing, voiceover, and background music.
Our videos aren&rsquo;t perfect yet, but we&rsquo;re always improving. We&rsquo;ve kept going without any funding till now, always bringing more videos to the community. If we get funding in the future, it will give us more resources and opportunities to produce better quality videos even faster.
Thanks for your support! Keep backing us, and we&rsquo;ll keep making awesome content for the community."))
