(json 181 (comment_id "629"))
(json 181 (user_id "312"))
(json 181 (proposal_id "5000"))
(json 181 (content "Hi Gombilla! Thanks a lot for your comments. We agree with you on the importance of ensuring the sustainability and long-term impact of the program beyond the initial workshops. We would like to share some of the strategies we have implemented and planned to address these concerns: <strong>1. #comunidadAPRENDO</strong> Upon graduation, participants don't end their journey with us; instead, they join&nbsp;<strong>#comunidadAPRENDO</strong>, a continuous learning community that offers ongoing personal and professional development opportunities. This community provides access to advanced courses through a <strong>learn2earn</strong> program called #criptoIMPULSO, which incentivizes continued participation by rewarding members for completing specific educational challenges. We will include AI-related courses in this program. <strong>2. SingularityNET-Specific Quests</strong>: We will introduce a set of SingularityNET-specific quests within <strong>#comunidadAPRENDO</strong>, offering hands-on experiences and practical engagement with the SingularityNET platform after the workshops themselves. These quests include activities such as completing surveys on AI interests, setting up SingularityNET accounts, using AI services, and creating AI project proposals. <strong>3. Continuous Support and Mentorship</strong>: Our program includes mechanisms for ongoing support and mentorship. Graduates can access a network of peers and mentors within <strong>#comunidadAPRENDO</strong>, promoting a supportive environment that sustains their interest and motivation in pursuing further learning and development opportunities in blockchain and AI. <strong>4. Leveraging the SingularityNET Latam Community</strong>: We will leverage the vibrant SingularityNET Latam community to provide additional support, networking opportunities, and resources. This collaboration will help sustain participants' engagement and offer a broader range of learning and development opportunities within the SingularityNET ecosystem. These are a few of the strategies we are putting together and are confident that they will extends the impact of the program well beyond the initial workshops. Let me know if you have another comment. Cheers!"))
