(json 222 (proposal_id "5066"))
(json 222 (content "Hi there. This is great. I would also add that although leveraging AWS services provides scalability and reliability, it's essential to monitor and optimize costs, especially as the system scales. Overlooking cost management could lead to unexpected expenses and budget overruns. Thanks !"))
