(json 224 (proposal_id "5451"))
(json 224 (content "Thank you for your insightful feedback. We appreciate your emphasis on the importance of aligning with SingularityNET's values . As part of our selection process, we will conduct thorough reviews of potential Key Opinion Leaders' backgrounds to ensure they truly resonate with SingularityNET's mission and ethics. This careful vetting will help us maintain the integrity and effectiveness of our outreach efforts."))
