(json 225 (comment_id "585"))
(json 225 (user_id "573"))
(json 225 (proposal_id "5556"))
(json 225 (content "Hi Gombilla,
Thank you for your insightful feedback. At Hunko, we are committed to providing personalized learning experiences while ensuring the utmost privacy and security for our users. To address your concerns, I'd like to clarify that we do not collect personal data such as names, ages, or email addresses. Instead, we gather data solely to create an educational profile that is not associated with any individual person, ensuring that the information we collect is not sensitive.
Nonetheless, to ensure robust information security, we will conduct a thorough analysis of the entire process to guarantee data protection at every stage. Our priority is to build user trust and comply with all data protection regulations.
Thanks again for your feedback and understanding.
Best regards,
Valentin"))
(json 225 (comment_votes "0"))
