(json 226 (user_id "138"))
(json 226 (proposal_id "5181"))
(json 226 (content "Thank you again Gombilla for your support and time spent on reviewing our proposal and your constructive feedback. much appreciated. Security and compliance will be our main focus on integration."))
(json 226 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 226 (created_at "2024-06-04 20:03:38"))
(json 226 (updated_at "2024-06-04 20:03:38"))
(json 227 (comment_id "583"))
(json 227 (user_id "576"))
(json 227 (proposal_id "5144"))
(json 227 (content "Thank you for your thoughtful message and for highlighting the concerns regarding the authenticity of AI-powered avatars and the associated ethical considerations. At Twin Protocol, we deeply share your commitment to maintaining high ethical standards and ensuring transparency and fairness in all our AI initiatives.
We understand the importance of authenticity in representing musicians' personalities and artistic styles. To address this, we ensure that our AI Twins are developed with the utmost respect for the original artist's consent and input, guaranteeing that their digital avatars remain true to their unique identity. Additionally, we will prioritize clear communication with fans about how their data is used, reinforcing our dedication to accountability and ethical interactions.
Our robust security protocols and ethical guidelines are designed to protect the integrity of both the artists and their fans, ensuring a trustworthy and enriching experience for all. We are excited about the potential of this collaboration and are committed to upholding these values as we move forward together."))
(json 227 (comment_votes "0"))
