(json 228 (proposal_id "5117"))
(json 228 (content "Hey Gombilla 👋
Regarding Roblox Accessibility:
It's available on almost all devices and also has support for VR. Roblox as a platform also gives a very smooth experience to its end users, meanwhile my team will also be ensuring that the game optimises the user-side memory allocation so that game runs smoothly on every device.
You also don't need a very fast internet for Roblox, a stable connection would do just fine as I have been testing that with many groups from different countries having different bandwidth."))
