(json 229 (proposal_id "5508"))
(json 229 (content "Thanks for the comment!
For what concerns the technical expertise required: I am an academic researcher in the field of adversarial robustness, and have previously published highly mathematical work on the topic (see my profile page). While of course there are no certainties in R&amp;D, I'd argue that my past experience has given me the tools to bring such a project to conclusion.
On user-friendliness and accessibility: indeed, we're keeping user-friendliness as a priority, which is why we're working on a proper programmer interface that can abstract away the complexities of robustness benchmarking.
Thanks again!
Celery"))
