(json 231 (comment_id "579"))
(json 231 (user_id "746"))
(json 231 (proposal_id "5345"))
(json 231 (content "Thank you Gombilla for your feedback. Indeed as you note we have set ourselves a daunting challenge, but also one we believe is critical to the welfare of humanity and the future of mankind. With the rapid development of AI technologies, we are reaching an inflection point. We must somehow manage to join forces and devise feasible ways to redistribute wealth and let all of humanity enjoy at least some of the fruits of such technological breakthroughs. This is not only about equal economic opportunities but also about releasing hundreds of millions if not billions of human minds from being busy in everyday survival, letting them learn, explore, and create. This is our chance to recruit and augment the intelligence and imagination of all humans and with the help of AI step forward to the next step of the evolution of human civilization. Indeed this invites a long-term vision and committing resources towards its actuation. &nbsp; &nbsp;"))
(json 231 (comment_votes "0"))
