(json 254 (comment_id "556"))
(json 254 (user_id "532"))
(json 254 (proposal_id "5281"))
(json 254 (content "Dear Gombilla,&nbsp;
To be candid we did expect that the comment section of this proposal would be the very place where we started to glean insights into people's expectations and Interpretations of the project.
&nbsp;
Thank you for all the salient points you have made, your thoughts are so encompassing and considerate.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Privacy is a big deal, and the project has multiple use cases, however be that as it may we already imagine every user will be able to set their privacy considerations ans determine how their ghost is used.
&nbsp;
In the event that a person decides to create a ghost from his imagination, we should have compliance and regulations that does guide such protocols.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Ethics is one of the biggest reasons we are going on this Ideation journey.
&nbsp;
Grieving is definitely one of the human behaviours that could be impacted by our project, we will seek expert counsel on the matter and adopt and adapt accordingly.
&nbsp;
People can decide they do not want to be&nbsp; ghost, in fact no one will be able to access your information enough to make a ghost out of it.
And depending on the use case scenarios we believe that their will be adequate regulations and restrictions to make sure the project is safe for everyone. We will ideate efficiently to this end.
&nbsp;
Thank you so much for your time. If you can please do review us a five seeing we have your mind blown. 😁
&nbsp;
Thank you for time"))
