(json 256 (comment_id "554"))
(json 256 (user_id "532"))
(json 256 (proposal_id "5625"))
(json 256 (content "Hi Gombilla,
Always a pleasure to read from you. You are right on all accounts. Quality tv production is expensive.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
We have however mitigated on these costs by using stars that we discover ourselves through the auditioning process, that way we pay for the jobs and not the stardom.
&nbsp;
Secondly, we are using YouTube distribution for now, our goals is to use evergreen stories and scenarios and to make sure that there is no subscription payment barrier stopping as many people as possible from accessing the stories.
Once we have gained subsequent traction with the first set of series, we can reach more people by accepting sponsorship or endorsement deals from SNET based solutions.
&nbsp;
These are how we have positioned ourself to address the valid concerns as you have pointed out.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Thank you Gombilla, for being so amazing. Please do give us a review, we wonder if we can get a five from you.
&nbsp;"))
