(json 344 (content "Hello Emotublockchain, thank you for your question.&nbsp;What sets FinGur&uacute; apart from other solutions is our dual focus on education and innovation. Unlike traditional media, we do not adhere to a strict editorial line, which allows for a diverse range of voices and opinions. Our agile structure enables us to rapidly implement technological advancements, fostering continuous innovation. This approach has facilitated significant user growth and engagement, currently reaching over 200,000 individuals across social media platforms like Instagram, X (formerly Twitter), LinkedIn, and TikTok. Additionally, we have established agreements with universities in Argentina (UCA, UBA, UTN, UADE), the government, and private entities to help them with innovation and education. Finally, our technical team, responsible for developing our AI products, has won national and international awards.If you have any other question or comment let me know,&nbsp;Best regards."))
