(json 383 (comment_id "421"))
(json 383 (user_id "33"))
(json 383 (proposal_id "4516"))
(json 383 (content "The concept is quite simple: to build an open source Identity and Trust Registry agent, which can be integrated into any project by calling simple APIs. This agent will be able to issue Digital Identity (on blockchain), issue Credentials, and Verify Credentials. When integrated, AIs will receive a Digital Identity, and at each execution of the service, a Credential will be issued to all those which take part of the service (the AI but also all its service providers). Anybody else will then be able to see proof of activity, performance, and reputation of the AI and its service providers, at any point in time.
Kind regards - Eric"))
