(json 399 (content "Hello Alen, I'm fine, thanks. Yeah, I'm from Brazil, is nice to meet you.
In a first moment, all patient data will be saved with their awareness and they will have the power to remove the data at any time. To improve our model, we need diagnostic data, but in no way will we link this to the person, so it will not be possible to identify a person based on a diagnosis. All this information will be in the platform's usage rules, but they are not final decisions, we are open to necessary adaptations to obtain the best result, following general data protection laws."))
