(json 417 (proposal_id "6263"))
(json 417 (content "Hello, and thank you for the time submitting this interesting proposal.I just have 2 question, step 1 is <strong>Model Compatibility and Integration</strong>: Ensuring that Quatern.ai models are compatible with the SingularityNET protocol, including adapting the API interfaces and data exchange formats.What happens if incompatibility is found.&nbsp;Second question, is wondering whether LLM type AI services can be integrated with the Quatern.ai protocol, like RAG and other addons, or what type of services can be used.I like this project direction, and hope there is opportunity for this plan to happen."))
