(json 460 (proposal_id "6256"))
(json 460 (content "Firstly, thanks for your comment, Tommy. Sencondly, our team have 2 proposal in this DF4. All is about Marketing initiatives, but one is on Youtube and another is on Tiktok. About your question:&nbsp;<em>how does it meet the primary rule for the Marketing pool - &nbsp;<strong>Purpose</strong>: To expand the&nbsp;<strong>Deep Funding ecosystem</strong>&nbsp;by increasing community engagement, attracting new users, and supporting ongoing community projects that align with&nbsp;<a href=https://singularitynet.io/ rel=nofollow ugc>SingularityNET's</a> goals of creating a democratic and decentralized AI landscape.</em> &nbsp; Our team envisions the impact of our proposal to be similar to the butterfly effect, through the content of our high-quality videos: Initially, the Vietnamese community will become aware of the existence, vision, and potential of SingularityNET and DF. The community includes diverse groups (for example, web3 users, AI enthusiasts, developers both within and outside the AI field, etc.). After becoming acquainted with SingularityNET and DF, the community may assess their capabilities and strengths to determine their potential roles within the ecosystem, such as reviewers, or directly submitting proposals in future DFs. If there are any further suggestions, please share them; our team is always eager to receive feedback from everyone."))
