(json 463 (proposal_id "5652"))
(json 463 (content "Here is a link to our website where we have already had talks about cinema and technology and throughout the year we have to continue promoting an information system about AI, Blockchain and the importance of approaching technology for the optimization of tedious processes and prioritization and focuses on the creative process.
https://www.lasfloresfilmfestival.com/events"))
