(json 485 (proposal_id "5752"))
(json 485 (content "Hi HenriqC, thank you for the comment!
Data is collected in real-time from wearables and health apps, processed through scalable pipelines, and securely stored using cloud solutions and blockchain for integrity and privacy. The core analytics layer uses LLM for natural language processing and simulating user behaviors, and RL for personalized health recommendations. Machine learning models provide predictive analytics for proactive health management. The user engagement layer features intuitive mobile/web applications, a gamified health-to-earn rewards system, and real-time interaction through a virtual health coach."))
