(json 491 (proposal_id "5777"))
(json 491 (content "Development of the MVP will take approximately 4 months, part of this would also be conversations with Rejuve to understand 1) if they would like us as a feature in their app, and 2) what should Of Nectar look like to entice users to actively participate.
I did not want to bog down the ideation application with technical requirements, and thus we see a lack thereof in the ideation proposal. Since the goal of this ideation project is in fact an MVP I wanted to allow us flexibility during development to meet both the timeline and the requirements for recording, and visualizing, appropriately the social clinical trials. The full application to come in future cycles will feature more indepth technical details as we finalize feedback from Rejuve, and the community throughout our ideation proposal horizon.&nbsp;"))
