(json 511 (updated_at "2024-05-19 18:11:54"))
(json 512 (comment_id "287"))
(json 512 (user_id "335"))
(json 512 (proposal_id "4770"))
(json 512 (content "Thank you for your feedback on our proposal! To address your concerns: &nbsp;&nbsp;

<strong>Business Focus</strong>: AdaLink specializes in developing marketing tools and products. We are developing a blockchain-based Affiliate Network on Cardano that facilitates partnership management by connecting stake pool operators and businesses with creators and marketers. More about our business can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=https://adalink.gitbook.io/adalink rel=nofollow ugc>AdaLink GitBook</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;
<strong>Creators Club and Ecosystem</strong>: We also manage the Frenchies by AdaLink, a dynamic creators' club with over 100 members, aimed at boosting promotional activities within the Web 3 and Cardano community.&nbsp;&nbsp;
<strong>Singularity News Show Budget</strong>: The budget for the Singularity News show, proposed at $3,333 per episode, is to cover a professional production that can range&nbsp;<em><strong>from 5 to 20 minutes</strong></em>. This budget is quite conservative for the industry, considering the professional standards we adhere to, which include pre-production planning to determine the show&rsquo;s format and content scope based on monthly events and developments.&nbsp;
<strong>Relevant Experience</strong>: Our team brings over 20 years of combined experience in television and commercial advertising. You can view our team's credentials on LinkedIn and IMDb via the links provided in the proposal. &nbsp;

We have carefully reviewed all community feedback and refined the budget to clearly outline the expenses for each milestone, specifying allocations for resources, cast, crew, contributors, and production costs. Additionally, we've shifted our focus from a full 6-month series to producing a high-quality pilot episode as a proof of concept. This adjustment results in a higher cost per episode due to one-time expenses such as creating the brand book, motion graphics, and other initial expenses, which do not recur in subsequent episodes. This change is designed to more effectively demonstrate the project's viability to the community. &nbsp;
Thank you again for your valuable comments!"))
(json 512 (comment_votes "0"))
