(json 564 (comment_id "231"))
(json 564 (user_id "37"))
(json 564 (proposal_id "4880"))
(json 564 (content "Thanks for your thoughtful comments. As regards your recommendations for a more encompassing biodiversity database, our team is keen on leveraging on a wide range of existing data and information on various bidioversity. Information from these existing resources will be added to our research outcomes, providing a more comprehensive repository on biodiversity. Also, data collection will be a continuous process, allowing us to iterate our database and broaden its contents. We appreciate your inputs as they help refine our proposal's landmarks.
Kind regards !
<em><strong>BIOTEK NEXUS Team</strong></em>"))
(json 564 (comment_votes "0"))
