(json 565 (user_id "30"))
(json 565 (proposal_id "4663"))
(json 565 (content "Kenn nothing trumps experiential learning, and that is what solutions like the one you are building are very effective for, students or whoever will be using this solution will benefit by being more conscious and taking responsible actions towards preserving mangroves. What I would love to know is the opensource strategy of the project as I would love to know if others can build on top of it, but overall very good project"))
