(json 566 (proposal_id "4880"))
(json 566 (content "Clement this is a well-written ideation project I must say, I love that you are able to show the transition from this idea to be project and what we should be expecting as assets that will go to the Ai marketplace, and its beautiful seeing you take the advice given to you here into account.&nbsp;Just to add that for a project of this magnitude, at ideation stage try to get diverse biodiversity as much as you can, this will help expand the possibilities and the approach you will take in this project, great job"))
