(json 569 (proposal_id "5245"))
(json 569 (content "Hi you present this proposal as though it were meant for the New project pool, two things here1. The goal of ideation is to prep research for projects that will go into the New project pool in next round, your proposal does not state what will be put in the new project pool next round2. It does not state an explicit AI service which will come out of this"))
