(json 571 (proposal_id "5117"))
(json 571 (content "We haven't putted it in the New Projects as we are not utilizing or making a new Ai Service rather using gamification techniques to publicize Deepfunding to a whole different community&nbsp;Thanks for the suggestions :) will add explanations regarding those terms in the proposal&nbsp;"))
