(json 571 (created_at "2024-05-16 16:59:30"))
(json 571 (updated_at "2024-05-16 16:59:30"))
(json 572 (comment_id "223"))
(json 572 (user_id "191"))
(json 572 (proposal_id "4503"))
(json 572 (content "Hi guys, nice to see you are making progress. The service itself looks good and the plan is understandable. I&rsquo;m just thinking how difficult it is to gain market share (though I know nothing about your market segment), but yea indeed if you make it, there are great opportunities to scale and bring a lot of activity on the SNET platform as well.&nbsp;
<strong>&nbsp;</strong>
&nbsp; &nbsp;Here are some questions that came to my mind: Are you planning some kind of reputation system for participants and if yes how would it work? How would your predictive maintenance system work? Are there factors such as brand, age, driven kilometers, maybe integrations into cars&rsquo; monitoring systems and maintenance history etc ? Could it include user observations and feedback?
<strong>&nbsp;</strong>
&nbsp; &nbsp;As you list the &ldquo;Recommendation Systems&rdquo; in the &lsquo;AI services (New or Existing)&rsquo; -section, I assumed you are going to create the recommendation algorithm by yourself and then launch it on the SNET marketplace. However in your response to Aokishi&rsquo;s comment you say that you are not going to develop any new AI services. So what exactly is your plan regarding the recommendation system ? If such a system is not yet available on the SNET platform and you will not build one by yourself, how are you going to get it?&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;The final question: What is the expected timeline for the project?
&nbsp;"))
(json 572 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 572 (created_at "2024-05-16 15:58:08"))
(json 572 (updated_at "2024-05-16 15:58:08"))
(json 573 (comment_id "222"))
(json 573 (user_id "13"))
(json 573 (proposal_id "5253"))
(json 573 (content "Clustering AI and human-written texts around the same topic is tricky because AI often repeats the same old ideas. To really capture unique insights, we can use smart NLP tools to dig deeper than just the words used and find the real themes. Plus, adding a way to spot the really unique stuff helps us spot fresh, human-like insights in the mix. This approach lets us blend AI's quick processing with the genuine creativity of human thoughts."))
(json 573 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 573 (created_at "2024-05-16 14:58:57"))
(json 573 (updated_at "2024-05-16 14:58:57"))
(json 574 (comment_id "221"))
(json 574 (user_id "37"))
(json 574 (proposal_id "4757"))
(json 574 (content "Thanks so much for your great insights. We find this really encouraging. In addition, we appreciate your insights on incorporating new approaches such as rearable health tech devices to propel our approach for data collection and aggregation. Our team is committed to continuous improvement, iteration and refinement. Our team will consider this your recommendations as a futuristic approach in our execution strategies. Once again, we welcome further contributions from you and the community, as they are important in refining our strategies.
&nbsp;
Kind regards !
<em><strong>AI4M Dev Team</strong></em>"))
(json 574 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 574 (created_at "2024-05-16 14:22:14"))
(json 574 (updated_at "2024-05-16 14:22:14"))
(json 575 (comment_id "220"))
(json 575 (user_id "191"))
(json 575 (proposal_id "5245"))
(json 575 (content "Hi, &nbsp;There is indeed a big change coming in this regard. A piece of data has never been an asset while a pile of data has. Due to the lack of infrastructure, the market mechanism hasn&rsquo;t been able to work properly. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Implementing your vision would incentivize one&rsquo;s choices towards more meaningful decisions and recording actions that one believes are valuable. Importantly, it encourages being unique and different, being oneself. As you say that your dream is to make browsing a universal source of income, I&rsquo;d expand that statement and make <em><strong>living</strong></em> a universal source of income. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Do you have any potential preliminary candidates for technology you might be applying in the project? I&rsquo;m a huge fan of the Midnight protocol for its privacy preserving smart contract capability although it hasn&rsquo;t reached its full maturity quite yet. Regarding AI integrations, the proposal currently states that LLMs will play a key part in the project. Even though this is still an ideation stage proposal I hope you could try to clarify a bit some potential ways they could be used on the user and the enterprise-user side. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Anyway, you are working on fixing a critical bug in our social systems and I wish you a lot of success! &nbsp;"))
(json 575 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 575 (created_at "2024-05-16 14:04:07"))
(json 575 (updated_at "2024-05-16 14:04:07"))
(json 576 (comment_id "219"))
(json 576 (user_id "191"))
(json 576 (proposal_id "4757"))
(json 576 (content "Great groundwork for the proposal beginning from Round 3! I love the fact that you have a clear use case even though the infrastructure itself can scale over any disease category and even beyond that. I can imagine countless parties who would benefit from and pay for accurate predictions in these areas.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; In the proposal you list many good sources of data and I&rsquo;d like to add one extra category. Wearable health tech devices are probably the first ones to know when the person is becoming sick. The number of people who are wearing some kind of health tracker is exploding. I recall a few years ago there was even a study where changes in the phone use habits could tell if there is an upcoming health issue.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To access this type of data at scale I think you have to find a way to make yourself accessible in applications that utilize privacy preserving data sharing solutions where people can monetize their data without giving it away (or you becoming a custodian of it).&nbsp; Fortunately this field is evolving rapidly and you are probably much more aware of it than me. <a href=https://medium.com/tap-in-with-taptools/iagon-unveils-mvp-for-health-data-privacy-on-the-midnight-network-3f933c59fa3a rel=nofollow ugc>Here</a> is a link to one actor&rsquo;s common sense explanation of the topic if someone is interested. I bet individuals would be more than willing to contribute with their spontaneously generating data if they can get a proper compensation for it.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Finally, I want to say that your proposal with its AI services is very well aligned with the goals of Deep Funding and the growth of the AI platform. I wish you success! &nbsp;"))
(json 576 (comment_votes "0"))
(json 576 (created_at "2024-05-16 13:29:59"))
(json 576 (updated_at "2024-05-16 13:29:59"))
(json 577 (comment_id "218"))
(json 577 (user_id "259"))
(json 577 (proposal_id "4515"))
(json 577 (content "Hi, thanks for your question!Since Sentience and Rejuve as exisit it was proposed it should go in Misc.&nbsp;I hope you enjoy our proposal and if you have more questions I'm here to answer.&nbsp;"))
