(json 578 (user_id "191"))
(json 578 (proposal_id "5253"))
(json 578 (content "Much needed service definitely. This is slightly off topic to this proposal but do you have any experience of how clustering based on diversity of the text content might work when there is AI generated content and human written content around the same topic? As humans are currently much better at coming up with genuine insights in open domains, most of the AI created content tends to center around the same perspectives even if their linguistic expression may be rich. The marginal benefit of a diverse insight is higher than in the case if the insight was not different from others."))
