(json 586 (proposal_id "4660"))
(json 586 (content "[edited] Excellent questions. In essence I'd like to build an intelligent platform built around the core missions and technology of SingularityNET.&nbsp;As we look towards building a beneficial AGI, I wish to establish a platform encouraging our innate ambitious curiosity. Collaborations and educational presentations from groups like Rejuve and Sophiaverse. A peculiar challenge to me of this new category is to shake off my preconceptions of what is allowed for Deep Funding. &nbsp;Seeing now that other proposals are about learning platforms, I've re-oriented my project towards my long-held dream of immersive, adventurous, ambitious learning in a 3D universe. Thank you very much for looking at my proposal and asking these questions this early in the competition.&nbsp;"))
