(json 633 (content "Surely, Milestone #2 the payment there is to secure a place to work and gather since we are talking about a State having a program to develop in the state for the state, people have said there should be a company ready to liason and to me that is a given then Singularity should take over being benefactor in aide while exchanging personnel of robotic embodiement, control algorithms, visual learning, language &amp; dialogue, cognitive modeling, behavorial research and planning policy, creating agreements between however many involved.&nbsp; In the milestone #2 is the place where we call Singularity's specific collab shop, should come very fast after seeing what is the smartest move for a safe Open Work Space.&nbsp; Also we will be getting ready being in Service with NY early on in their possible transitions.&nbsp; Further more, really I would like to be an arm for Singularity cultivating these agreement deals, also a flow of a younger generation becoming Singulatarians with good different combination events I see down the line as well. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;"))
