(json 644 (proposal_id "4865"))
(json 644 (content "Thank you for your opinion. We've made some adjustments to the content of the proposal based on your question. First, I thank you for understanding me because English is not my mother tongue. Second, we organized SingularityNET Talk via Zoom, not an offline event. We will work on engaging our existing users who are in groups interested in Cardano. Through Talk sessions, we will help members better understand SingularityNET and Deep Funding. Hope I have answered your question correctly."))
