(json 645 (proposal_id "4880"))
(json 645 (content "Hi there !. Thanks so much for your thoughtful insights on our proposal. In swift response, our proposing team have been able to make some adjustments in relation to your comments.&nbsp; First, we have included in the core problem section and the section which preceeds it, the fact that our proposal will be geared towards further development of our ideas which will then be reintroduced into the subsequent new project pool for the next funding round.
We have also added more information on our team section but are limited to character count (kindly assess seperate project team segment to get more details).&nbsp;
In relation to your observations on our deliverables, we have made inclusions on our core intiatives (carbon credit market and citizens eco science space) in the first and second milestones but have generalized it under research and technical documentation.&nbsp;
Also, we have included in the long description section of our proposal, the future scope of this proposal in relation to the community's engagement.&nbsp;
We appreciate you and look forward to more inputs from you and the rest of the community as they are valuable in shaping our proposal's landscape.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Kind Regards !
<strong><em>BIOTEK NEXUS Team</em></strong>"))
