(json 648 (content "I was a reviewer of your past proposal and your work. I applaud your proposal here and your detailed Team info. I would like to revisit and Review and rate this proposal but I would request two things from you first. I understand English is not your native language so I can appreciate the nuances of misspellings and grammer issues. I would suggest to polish the writing during this period so voters see a solid proposal.
