(json 656 (proposal_id "4525"))
(json 656 (content "The main technical challenges in integrating AI and blockchain technology into PadiWash's existing car care infrastructure include:
1. Data integration and interoperability between AI algorithms and blockchain systems.2. Scalability of AI models and blockchain transactions to handle growth.3. Security and privacy protection for sensitive customer data and transactions.4. Complex smart contract development for automated services.5. Regulatory compliance regarding data protection and financial transactions.
To address these challenges, PadiWash aim to collaborate with SingularityNET decentralized AI marketplace for AI solutions, we will also research and evaluate a scalable blockchain architectures while implementing robust security measures, and establishing a compliance framework."))
