(json 677 (proposal_id "4138"))
(json 677 (content "Due to feedback in the ratings section I have updated open source question to MIT open source license. In the first submission I missed it, just an honest mistake. 
Also, I want to mention here regarding latest review by Rafael_Cardoso on rating section. The current proposal is a test simulation of current voting system on DF portal with/out Weighted liquid rank reputation system. This tool will compare the current voting metrics with/out quadratic voting to weighted liquid rank. Variables involved are all the activities by users like votes, wallet size, likes, comments, and other correlations which will be discovered after the complete analysis of input dataset. Regarding flexibility of the tool, it would accommodate future upgrades in the voting portal including updates in voting methodology, addition of metrics or combinations of metrics."))
