(json 681 (content "Impactful project indeed! Good questions and good answers in the discussion. Thanks!

Here is one more question: How do you think it might be possible to incorporate and leverage the user feedback for improving the accuracy of the model? I guess many users will be relatively motivated, know what they are looking for and would happily share their insights."))
