(json 715 (proposal_id "4001"))
(json 715 (content "Jan let me clarify perhaps the use of AI behind this product.   The Metahug team will not be building AI, however what they are building will be a novel front-end allowing creative utilization of a number of AI services that Jam Galaxy will put on the SNet platform.  For starters this will be the AI Synthesizer and the Desdemona Voice Model.  These two AI services will be accessed via API on the back end of the Galactic Jam Machine game, allowing the game to be used with novel AI-generated sounds (in addition to the default Cosmic Sounds that the game will come with).

So basically from an AI perspective this is a way of making cool AI music tools such as JG's tools available in a game form to Roblox players, rather than just to musicians...."))
(json 715 (comment_votes "3"))
